American Muslim groups are using [online video in a collaborative
project](http://www.myfaithmyvoice.com/about.php) to try and explain what
Islam is about in an attempt to defuse the rise of anti Islam racism and fear
spurned by a community center to be built near Ground Zero in New York City.
[Via.](http://osocio.org/message/the_fight_against_racism_gets_personal/)

